OL,3,CPort Talbot blast furnaces could close
OL,4,Cearly because of strike action, says
OL,5,CTata
OL,7,FTata Steel has told staff that both
OL,8,Fblast furnaces in Port Talbot will
OL,9,Fclose as early as 5 July if industrial
OL,10,Faction is not called off.
OL,12,FThe company had planned to close one
OL,13,Fof its blast furnaces before the end
OL,14,Fof June, with the other shutting down
OL,15,Fby September.
OL,17,FOn Friday, Unite the union called for
OL,18,Fhistoric strike action beginning on 8
OL,19,FJuly over green plans that would see
OL,20,Fthousands of job losses.
